description:
This is a 23 minute workout called 'Yoga For Hips & Lower Back Release  |  Yoga With Adriene' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This Yoga With Adriene practice invites you to go inward, uniting breath and body to cultivate balance.

Invite stability and welcome release.

Come on everyone.

Sigh it out today!

This seemingly simple practice has depth.

ENJOY!
